highlights.text: “Maan Meri Jaan” by King has been on Top Songs Jaipur the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
“Ek Din Pyaar” by MC STAN is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Jaipur, up 40 spots at #60.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Jaipur. “Jhoome Jo Pathaan” is the highest at #5.
“SPAIN” by Jassa Dhillon and thiarajxtt is the highest new entry on Top Songs Jaipur at #47.
